<P>
INTEREST RATE HIKES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Orange County goes bankrupt. Chalk up another win for Alan Greenspan's 
interest rate hikes. 
</P>
<P>
 OLIVER BERLINER 
</P>
<P>
 Beverly Hills 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA121694-0012 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 108521 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 16, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 6; Column 1; Letters Desk 
