<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA121694-0098 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 108607 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 16, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
