<HEADLINE>
<P>
WEST VALLEY FOCUS: CALABASAS; CITY SUES TO HALT AHMANSON EXTENSION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BARBARA MURPHY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The city of Calabasas has gone to court to block Ventura County's decision 
