<TEXT>
<P>
 Tyrone Butler scored the final four points of the game Thursday to lead Golden 
West to a 76-73 upset over Santa Monica, 10th-ranked in the state, in the first 
round of the Cypress men's basketball tournament. 
</P>
<P>
 Butler made a basket with 1:36 left to put Golden West ahead, 74-73, then 
sealed the victory by making two free throws with 10 seconds remaining. 
