<HEADLINE>
<P>
A LITTLE BIT OF HISTORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 High school football officials voted in May, 1986, to go on strike and did not 
settle with the Southern and City sections until Aug. 28 -- less than two weeks 
before the season. 
</P>
