</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 County restructuring -- A headline Thursday misidentified the official who 
called for the formation of a committee to make sweeping changes in county 
government operations. Supervisor Roger R. Stanton called for a downsizing of 
the county bureaucracy. 
</P>
