<TEXT>
<P>
 Reagan library -- An article Thursday incorrectly reported the expanded 
visiting hours for the Ronald Reagan Presidential Library during its World War 
II exhibit. The library will be open until 8 p.m. Wednesdays through Feb. 28. 
It closes at 5 p.m. all other days. 
</P>
